


   Angular - App
   --------------
   
   
     module(s)
     
      component(s) --> controller , filter , directive , service
      
     ----------------------------- 
     
     
     Unit Testing  
     E2E  Testing
     
     
     -----------------------------
     
     apply TDD or BDD style
     
     -----------------------------
     
     
     
     UniTesting
     -----------
     
     we need Testing F.W
     
       --> to write test-cases
       --> to run and generate reports
       
       
     some popular sTesting F.Ws for JS-lang
     
     1. jasmine
     2. mocha  with chai and sinon
     
     
     E2E Testing
     ------------
     
     using jasmine , we write e2e test-cases
     
     to run e2e test cases , we need 'protractor' test-runner which is based on 'selinuim server'
     
     
     e.g
     
     proj
     -------
     
        web-calculator using angular
        
     
        module:  calc
        
         comp: CalcController
     
     
     ---------------------------------
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     